#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:8
msgid "Marknote"
msgstr "Marknote"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:9
msgid "Write down your thoughts"
msgstr "Annota tu pensamentos"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:11
msgid ""
"Marknote lets you create rich text notes and easily organise them into "
"notebooks. You can personalise your notebooks by choosing an icon and accent "
"color for each one, making it easy to distinguish between them and keep your "
"notes at your fingertips. Your notes are saved as Markdown files in your "
"Documents folder, making it easy to use your notes outside of Marknote as "
"well as inside the app."
msgstr ""
"Marknote te permitte crear notas de ric texto e facilemente organisar los in "
"quadernos. Tu pote personalisar tu quadernos per seliger un icone e color de "
"accento per cata un, facente facile dinstinguer inter illos e mantener tu "
"notas a tu extremitate de digito. Tu sotas es salveguardate como files de "
"Markdown in tu dossier Documento, facente facile usar tu notas foras de "
"Marknote tanto como intra le app."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:36
msgid ""
"Small bug fix release, mainly to fix deleting notebooks and some other minor "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Parve edition de correction de errores, principalmente pro corriger le "
"deletion de libros de notas (notebooks)  e alcun altere parve modificationes."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:42
msgid ""
"Marknote 1.5.1 contains various bug fixes, including the ones for specific "
"issues while coping and pasting. This release also adds some tiny "
"improvements like syntax highlighting in the source mode and faster image "
"loading."
msgstr ""
"Marknote 1.5.1 contine varie correctiones de errores, includite illos pro "
"problemas specific durante le copiar e collar. Iste version etiam adde alcun "
"parve melioramentos como le evidentiar de syntaxe in le modo de fonte e un "
"cargamento de imagines  plus rapide."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:48
msgid ""
"Marknote 1.5 introduces major new features like Source Mode for raw Markdown "
"editing, cross-notebook wiki-style links, and a KRunner plugin for quickly "
"opening notes from the Plasma desktop. The release also improves note "
"organization, editor auto-formatting, media handling, UI animations, and "
"overall stability with many quality-of-life updates and bug fixes."
msgstr ""
"Marknote 1.5 introduce nove grane characteristicas como Source Mode (Modo de "
"Fonte) per editar crude Markdown, ligamines de quadernos-cruciate de stilo "
"wiki, e un plugin de KRunner per aperir rapidemente notas ex scriptoprio de "
"Plasma. Le livration anque meliora organisation de nota, formatar automatic "
"de editor, manear media, animationes de UI, estabilitate general con multe "
"actualisationes de qualitate de vita e correctiones de faltas."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:55
msgid ""
"This release contains a large number of bug fixes and small improvements."
msgstr ""
"Iste version contine un grande numero de correctiones de faltas e parve "
"melioramentos."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:59
msgid "You can now undo and redo changes in the quick sketch dialog"
msgstr ""
"Tu pote nunc annullare refacer cambiamentos in le dialogo de schizzo rapide"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:60
msgid "You can now drag and drop images"
msgstr "Tu pote ora traher e poner images"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:61
msgid "The main view no longer disappears when resizing sidebars"
msgstr ""
"Le vista principal nonplus disappare quando on redimensiona barras lateral"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:62
msgid "Issues with delete dialogs have been fixed"
msgstr "Problemas con ledialogos de delre ha essite corrigite"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:69
msgid ""
"On small phone screens, you want as much space as possible to write and read "
"your notes. Marknote now lets you hide the editor toolbar on mobile, so you "
"can focus on the important stuff while having the formatting options just a "
"tap away."
msgstr ""
"Sur parve schermos de telephono,tu vole le plus spatio possibile per scriber "
"e leger tu notas.Marknote nunc te permitte celar le editor sur mobile,assi "
"que tu pote focalisar sur le cosa importante dum haber le optiones de "
"formatar sol distante un colpo."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:75
msgid ""
"On desktop, you can now adjust the width of the note list and editor by "
"dragging the separator, just like in other desktop applications."
msgstr ""
"Sur scriptorio,to ora pote adaptar le largessa del lista de nota e del "
"editor per traher le separator, juste comoin altere applicationes de "
"scriptorio. "

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:79
msgid ""
"You can now undo and redo changes using buttons in the UI, rather than "
"relying on keyboard shortcuts, which is especially helpful if you're using a "
"virtual keyboard that may not have a control key. The application menu has "
"been reorganized and simplified to make it less cluttered."
msgstr ""
"Tu pote ora annullar e facer cambiamentos usante buttones in le UI,plus "
"tosto que depender sur vias breve de claviero, lo que es specialmente de "
"adjuta si tu es usante un claviero virtual que pote non haber un clave de "
"controlo. Le menu de application ha essire reorganisate e simplificate per "
"facer lo minus incombrate."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:87
msgid ""
"We added implemented clickable links! You can now ctrl-click links to open "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Nos addeva ligamines cliccabile implementate! Tu nunc pote usar ctrl-clicca "
"per aperir los."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:90
msgid ""
"To make it easier to switch from your current notes application to Marknote, "
"Marknote now offers several import options. For now you can import your "
"notes from KNotes and maildir."
msgstr ""
"Pro facer plus facile passar ex tu application currente de notas a Marknote, "
"Marknote ora offere multe optiones de importar. Actualmente tu pote importar "
"tu notas ex KNotes e maildir."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:99
msgid "Bug fixes release containing the following fixes:"
msgstr "Version de correctiones de bug,continente le sequente correctiones:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:101
msgid "Fix saving font"
msgstr "Corrige salveguardar font"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:102
msgid "Remember last window state"
msgstr "Memora le stato de ultime fenestra"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:103
msgid "Close dialog after deleting note"
msgstr "Claude dialogo post deler nota"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:104
msgid "Fix double copy paste"
msgstr "Corrige collar de duple copia"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:105
msgid "Fix sidebar not scrollable when there is a note books overflow"
msgstr "Corrige non rolabile quando il ha un disbordar de libros de nota"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:111
msgid ""
"We improved the notes management with the ability to choose a custom folder "
"where to store your notes and made it possible to change the sorting of "
"notes from alphabetically to by date. The sidebar is now collapsible and we "
"added a focus mode where everything but the text editor is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Nos meliorava le gestion de notas con le habilitate a seliger un dossier "
"personalisate ubi immagazinar tu notas e facer lo possibile cambiar le "
"ordine de notas ex alphabetically a per data. Le barra lateral es nunc "
"plicabile e nos addeva un modo de focalisar ubi toto preter le editor de "
"texto es monstrate."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:118
msgid ""
"If you prefer to just use Marknote as a Markdown editor, we made it possible "
"to just open any markdown files directly from the file browser or the "
"console. Additionally Marknote supports markdown files with a so called "
"front matter, which is a common way to inject metadata to markdown in static "
"website generators like Hugo and Jekyll."
msgstr ""
"Si tu prefere solmente usar Marknote como un editor de Markdown,nos lo face "
"possibile per solmente aperir ulle files de markdown directemente ab le "
"navigator de file o le console. Additionalmente Marknote supporta files de "
"markdown con un sinominate frontispicio,que es un modo commun per injectar "
"metadatos a markdown in generatores de sitos web static como Hugo e Jekill."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:126
msgid ""
"In term of edition support, the subset of markdown supported increased "
"again. Now it is possible to add and edit tables. Additionally we started "
"transforming inline markdown directly to rich text as you type. Support is "
"limited to a few markdown constructs but is likely to grow over time. You "
"can now customize the font used by editor."
msgstr ""
"In termino de supporto de edition,le sub-insimul de markdown supportate ha "
"augmentate novemente. Nunc il es possibile adder e editar tabellas. "
"Additionalmente nos startava transformar markdown integrate directemente a "
"texto ric durante que tu typa. Supporto es limitate a pauc constructos de "
"markdown ma probabilemente il crescera in le tempore. Tu pote ora "
"personalisar le font usate per le editor."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:134
msgid ""
"Aside from being able to edit text, it's now possible to also create "
"sketches directly from Marknote."
msgstr ""
"Al latere ab poter editar texto, il es nunc possibile anque crear schizzos "
"directemente ab Marknote."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:138
msgid ""
"Finally we took care of ensuring Marknote was fully usable when used with "
"Plasma Mobile."
msgstr ""
"Finalmente nos nos occupa de assecurar que Marknote esseva completemente "
"usabile quando usate con Plasma Mobile."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:146
msgid "Fix an important bug"
msgstr "Corrige un falta importante"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:152
msgid ""
"Marknote 1.1.0 is out! Marknote is the new WYSIWYG note-taking application "
"from KDE. Despite the latest release being just a few days ago, we have been "
"hard at work and added a few new features and, more importantly, fixed some "
"bugs."
msgstr ""
"Marknote 1.1.0 es sortite! Marknote es le nove appllication WYSIWYG de "
"prender notas de KDE. Nonobstante que le ultime version ha essite relaxate "
"sol alcun dies ante, nos ha facite un dur labor e addeva alcun nove "
"characteristicas e, plus importante, corrigeva alcun faltas."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:158
msgid ""
"Marknote now boasts broader Markdown support, and can now display images and "
"task lists in the editor. And once you are done editing your notes, you can "
"export them to various formats, including PDF, HTML and ODT."
msgstr ""
"Marknote nunc se vante de un aupporto de MArkdown plus large, e pote ora "
"monstrar images e traciar listas in le editor. E un vice que tu ha editate "
"tu notas, tu pote exporta los in varie formatos,includente PDF, HTML e ODT."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:164
msgid ""
"Marknote's interface now seamlessly integrates the colors assigned to your "
"notebooks, enhancing its visual coherence and making it easier to "
"distinguish one notebook from another. Additionally, your notebooks remember "
"the last opened note, automatically reopening it upon selection."
msgstr ""
"Le interfacie de Marknotes nunc integra perfectemente le colores assignate a "
"tu quaderno, augmentar su coherentia visual e facer plus facile distinguer "
"un quaderno ab un altere. Additionalmente,tu quadernos memora le ultime nota "
"aperite, reaperiente lo automaticamente sur selection."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:170
msgid ""
"We've also introduced a convenient command bar similar to the one in "
"Merkuro. This provides quick access to essential actions within Marknote. "
"Currently it only creates a new notebook and note, but we plan to make more "
"actions available in the future. Finally we have reworked all the dialogs in "
"Markdown to use the newly introduced FormCardDialog from KirigamiAddons."
msgstr ""
"Nos ha anque introducite un barra de commando convenibile simile a lo de "
"Merkuro. Isto forni rapide accesso a actiones essential intra Marknote. "
"Currentemente il crea solmente un nove quaderno e nota,ma nos planifica "
"facer disponibile plus actiones in le futuro. Al fin nos ha re-elaborate "
"tote le dialogos in Markdown per usar le recentemente introducite "
"FormCArdDialog ex KirigamiAddons."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:183
msgid ""
"Marknote, KDE's WYSIWYG note-taking application, is finally ready for it's "
"first release. Marknote lets you create rich text notes and easily organise "
"them into notebooks. You can personalise your notebooks by choosing an icon "
"and accent color for each one, making it easy to distinguish between them "
"and keep your notes at your fingertips. Your notes are saved as Markdown "
"files in your Documents folder, making it easy to use your notes outside of "
"Marknote as well as inside the app."
msgstr ""
"Marknote , application WYSIWYG de KDE per prender notas , es finalmente "
"preste per su prime version. Marknote te permitte crear notas de ric texto e "
"facilemente organisar los in quadernos. Tu pote personalisar tu quadernos "
"per seliger un icone e color de accento per cata un, facente facile "
"dinstinguer  inter illos e mantener tu notas a tu extremitate de digito. Tu "
"notas es salveguardate como files de Markdown in tu dossier Documento, "
"facente  facile usar tu notas foras de Marknote tanto como intra le app."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.marknote.metainfo.xml:193
msgid ""
"Thanks to Carl, Marknote now not only supports bold and italic fonts, but "
"also lets you underline important parts, strike out wrong parts, organise "
"your thoughts in various list types and organise your notes with titles, "
"sections and more."
msgstr ""
"Gratias a Carl, Marknote nonsolmente supporta fonts grasse e italic, ma "
"anque te permitte sublinear partes importante, cancellar partes errate, "
"organisar tu pensamentos in varie typos de lista e organisar tu notas con  "
"titulos,sectiones e plus."

